{"tid":2012467,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"棺材舞隊長：好想送細哨最後一程..............","createTime":"2020-05-11T15:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T16:27:35.000Z","uid":10338,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6456db28649eaf92b290d9868e7fd5ddd7d7fe7d","tid":2012467,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"「黑人棺材舞」近日在網絡爆紅，不少人打開Facebook等社交網站，都會突然見到有4至6名黑人穿上西裝，合力抬着一副棺材，然後跟住電子音樂舞曲起舞，場面詼諧。其實「黑人抬棺」源於非洲加納的喪禮，棺材舞隊長Benjamin Aidoo日前接受傳媒訪問時就表示，最希望送「細哨」朗拿甸奴最後一程。<br />\n<br />\nBenjamin Aidoo從事殯儀工作，他認為不一定要傷心地面對死亡，大家可以抱住慶祝生命的心態看待有人離世，所以就為客戶提戶這種別出心裁的服務。當被問到最希望為哪位球星「服務」時，身為巴塞隆拿與車路士球迷的Benjamin，就選擇了因為涉嫌使用假護照，目前被巴拉圭當局軟禁的一代巴西球王朗拿甸奴。他說：「我當然希望他們長命百歲，但如果有機會的話，我希望送朗拿甸奴最後一程，之後就是馬勒當拿，最後是美斯。朗拿甸奴一直是我很欣賞的球員。他是球場上的舞蹈家，而我將以舞蹈向他致敬。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管身為巴塞球迷，但Benjamin直言他非常討厭蘇亞雷斯，因為這名烏拉圭前鋒曾在2010年世界盃對加納的8強戰，於下半場補時階段蓄意用手護空門，加納最終在互射12碼階段被淘汰。他說：「每當我見到這個球員，甚至是聽到蘇亞雷斯這個名字，我會感到不快。他的手球令加納無法晉級4強，真的很可惡。我們這裏有個說法，蘇亞雷斯就代表『不可能』，如果你想做到一件事，但蘇亞雷斯出現了，就代表你不會成功。」"},{"pid":"6dfdc75c52a0da090972a0c983cc89a00d6c9c1d","tid":2012467,"uid":40757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"身為巴塞隆拿與車路士球迷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124d6ce38b218d2da92cebe8aa872b99bf85f1ef","tid":2012467,"uid":10338,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6dfdc75c52a0da090972a0c983cc89a00d6c9c1d","tid":2012467,"uid":40757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"身為巴塞隆拿與車路士球迷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"其實蘋果無講清楚<br />\n睇返英文個訪問<br />\n佢中意留意返加納D球員<br />\n所以中意艾辛<br />\n但真正中意應該巴塞"},{"pid":"7da62384bd9fbc2e47420530c405ca9285a71356","tid":2012467,"uid":46911,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ro9pKvC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRo9pKvC.gif&h=e6d9e8ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送疤一程"},{"pid":"b3daa561dd099b8cc8f55db048d74c5744665ea1","tid":2012467,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/e78eb9b513a7272accec72fb2977bdbf/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fe78eb9b513a7272accec72fb2977bdbf%2Ftenor.gif&h=b54539d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82ef8167e8b15703235ce8a8e433ea84b98b74dc","tid":2012467,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3daa561dd099b8cc8f55db048d74c5744665ea1","tid":2012467,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/e78eb9b513a7272accec72fb2977bdbf/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fe78eb9b513a7272accec72fb2977bdbf%2Ftenor.gif&h=b54539d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158404fe5b5cc7821d779f6d1a6ac7b61314645b","tid":2012467,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ef8167e8b15703235ce8